1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,288
[Third Stem Room]

2
00:00:06,139 --> 00:00:07,139
Master.

3
00:00:07,651 --> 00:00:09,685
We gave the business between Talhan
and the Central Plains

4
00:00:09,709 --> 00:00:10,944
to Boss Lin.

5
00:00:11,211 --> 00:00:13,331
Only then did she agree
to let us run her restaurant.

6
00:00:13,747 --> 00:00:15,849
Do you think it's worth it?

7
00:00:17,584 --> 00:00:18,584
It doesn't matter.

8
00:00:19,019 --> 00:00:20,053
In this way,

9
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:21,788
with these restaurants,

10
00:00:22,455 --> 00:00:23,455
we can be said to

11
00:00:23,656 --> 00:00:25,176
have our own territory in the capital.

12
00:00:25,792 --> 00:00:27,269
When it comes to sending
messages in the future,

13
00:00:27,293 --> 00:00:28,573
it will also be more convenient.

14
00:00:30,030 --> 00:00:31,030
By the way,

15
00:00:31,197 --> 00:00:32,277
did Boss Lin bring any news

16
00:00:32,532 --> 00:00:33,833
when she came back this time?

17
00:00:36,036 --> 00:00:39,305
The fourth prince who was previously
sent to the Northern Frontier

18
00:00:39,539 --> 00:00:41,041
was assassinated some time ago.

19
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:43,376
Although he didn't die,

20
00:00:43,410 --> 00:00:46,079
it seems that his legs were left disabled.

21
00:00:50,517 --> 00:00:51,717
I remember that two years ago,

22
00:00:52,118 --> 00:00:53,586
the third prince

23
00:00:54,187 --> 00:00:55,787
was also poisoned by miasma in his fief.

24
00:00:56,289 --> 00:00:57,609
If it were only the third prince,

25
00:00:58,324 --> 00:00:59,804
it could be said that he was unlucky.

26
00:01:00,794 --> 00:01:01,895
But the fourth prince

27
00:01:02,262 --> 00:01:05,165
also ended up like this just
one year after going to his fief.

28
00:01:08,134 --> 00:01:09,134
It seems like,

29
00:01:09,869 --> 00:01:10,909
it's all Yin Zhou's doing.

30
00:01:12,138 --> 00:01:14,007
Yin Zhou is truly ruthless.

31
00:01:14,073 --> 00:01:15,608
These third and fourth princes

32
00:01:15,642 --> 00:01:16,843
are his own younger brothers.

33
00:01:20,713 --> 00:01:21,713
A Qi

34
00:01:23,783 --> 00:01:24,783
is in danger.

35
00:01:25,718 --> 00:01:26,718
Wenjie,

36
00:01:26,986 --> 00:01:28,831
arrange a meeting with Boss Lin
for me as soon as possible.

37
00:01:28,855 --> 00:01:29,855
The sooner, the better.

38
00:01:30,457 --> 00:01:31,457
Yes, Master.

39
00:01:51,544 --> 00:01:52,544
Come in.

40
00:02:01,688 --> 00:02:04,023
This must be Boss Lin.

41
00:02:05,925 --> 00:02:06,925
I'm Pei Yanzhi, a junior.

42
00:02:07,227 --> 00:02:08,907
I've long admired your reputation, senior.

43
00:02:11,898 --> 00:02:12,898
Pei Yanzhi.

44
00:02:14,501 --> 00:02:15,635
As far as I know,

45
00:02:16,302 --> 00:02:18,004
your name is Feng Sun, isn't it?

46
00:02:20,140 --> 00:02:22,020
Indeed, nothing can be
hidden from you, senior.

47
00:02:23,510 --> 00:02:24,790
Let's get straight to the point.

48
00:02:25,354 --> 00:02:26,354
So,

49
00:02:26,746 --> 00:02:28,047
what do you want from me?

50
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:31,794
You're indeed a
straightforward person, senior.

51
00:02:31,818 --> 00:02:32,818
Then I'll be direct.

52
00:02:33,253 --> 00:02:34,573
I'll help you make money, senior.

53
00:02:34,654 --> 00:02:35,654
But at the same time,

54
00:02:35,678 --> 00:02:38,066
I need you
to help me train a group of death warriors.

55
00:02:38,698 --> 00:02:39,966
You're from Talhan.

56
00:02:40,807 --> 00:02:42,342
Why should I trust you

57
00:02:42,896 --> 00:02:45,298
that you won't use me against Daxing?

58
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,820
Because I need this group of death warriors

59
00:02:49,669 --> 00:02:51,104
just to protect someone.

60
00:02:55,842 --> 00:02:56,842
Yanzhi,

61
00:02:57,343 --> 00:02:58,645
you're a good child.

62
00:03:00,213 --> 00:03:02,315
I know this request is a bit excessive,

63
00:03:03,583 --> 00:03:04,584
but as a mother,

64
00:03:05,418 --> 00:03:06,685
I must arrange things
properly for my two children

65
00:03:06,686 --> 00:03:07,954
before I can rest easy.

66
00:03:09,722 --> 00:03:11,558
I left Granny Su with Heshu,

67
00:03:12,458 --> 00:03:13,578
and I feel somewhat at ease.

68
00:03:14,093 --> 00:03:15,528
But Qi'er is different.

69
00:03:15,795 --> 00:03:16,795
He's a prince.

70
00:03:17,330 --> 00:03:19,532
The slightest mishap
could cost him his life.

71
00:03:21,801 --> 00:03:23,281
Don't worry, Imperial Concubine Chen.

72
00:03:24,103 --> 00:03:25,463
No matter what situation we're in,

73
00:03:26,906 --> 00:03:28,186
I will protect the Fifth Prince.

74
00:03:29,409 --> 00:03:30,409
For the rest of my life,

75
00:03:32,445 --> 00:03:32,979
I will never go back on

76
00:03:33,012 --> 00:03:34,012
my promise.

77
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:10,300
"Journey With You"

78
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,200
(Episode 6)

79
00:06:04,097 --> 00:06:05,097
Yanzhi,

80
00:06:05,752 --> 00:06:07,553
I will definitely change
our fate.

81
00:06:08,167 --> 00:06:09,167
This time,

82
00:06:09,402 --> 00:06:11,304
no one can stop us from being together.

83
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:27,879
What's wrong?

84
00:07:28,314 --> 00:07:29,315
Has your wound opened again?

85
00:07:32,351 --> 00:07:33,553
It's not the wound that hurts.

86
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,159
Yanzhi,

87
00:07:50,243 --> 00:07:51,243
this time,

88
00:07:52,138 --> 00:07:53,473
we can be together

89
00:07:53,951 --> 00:07:55,552
without any reservations, right?

90
00:08:00,313 --> 00:08:01,313
It's just that

91
00:08:02,448 --> 00:08:04,483
we still have to put on
a big show for Yin Zhou.

92
00:08:10,356 --> 00:08:12,024
If you were to join a theater troupe,

93
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:13,959
you would definitely be

94
00:08:15,261 --> 00:08:16,863
a master at acting.

95
00:08:32,545 --> 00:08:33,778
Your Royal Highness, the Crown Prince,

96
00:08:33,779 --> 00:08:35,815
is unwilling to go to the
banquet at Yanbo Tower.

97
00:08:36,315 --> 00:08:38,551
Why is he putting on such airs today?

98
00:08:39,151 --> 00:08:40,219
What does this mean?

99
00:08:40,932 --> 00:08:43,035
I don't trust your good nephew.

100
00:08:43,756 --> 00:08:44,991
The Khan's intentions

101
00:08:45,491 --> 00:08:47,026
are also beyond my comprehension.

102
00:08:48,761 --> 00:08:49,862
Since that's the case,

103
00:08:50,696 --> 00:08:53,032
I won't beat around the bush.

104
00:08:54,166 --> 00:08:56,569
Nowadays, the Fifth
Prince is in the limelight.

105
00:08:57,436 --> 00:09:00,072
What do you plan to do?

106
00:09:00,740 --> 00:09:03,009
What do you need me to do?

107
00:09:06,579 --> 00:09:09,081
I don't understand what
the Khan means by this.

108
00:09:09,631 --> 00:09:11,299
I want to get to know the Khan

109
00:09:11,884 --> 00:09:14,120
because the Khan is a hero.

110
00:09:14,587 --> 00:09:15,922
But in the Khan's words,

111
00:09:15,946 --> 00:09:18,048
I've become a scheming person

112
00:09:18,891 --> 00:09:21,794
eager to use the Khan's power.

113
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:28,567
We all know what's going on.

114
00:09:29,068 --> 00:09:30,369
There's no need to hide it.

115
00:09:31,571 --> 00:09:33,306
With my full support,

116
00:09:34,073 --> 00:09:35,073
soon,

117
00:09:35,141 --> 00:09:37,777
you will go from being the Crown Prince

118
00:09:38,277 --> 00:09:39,912
to the Crown Prince Consort.

119
00:09:42,741 --> 00:09:43,775
These past few days,

120
00:09:44,597 --> 00:09:47,534
my fifth brother has been very restless.

121
00:09:48,387 --> 00:09:49,907
He's been gathering troops everywhere,

122
00:09:50,656 --> 00:09:52,158
attempting to rebel.

123
00:09:53,526 --> 00:09:54,660
I wonder if the Khan

124
00:09:55,595 --> 00:09:57,463
would be willing to give
me a group of troops

125
00:09:57,837 --> 00:09:59,837
to accompany me to protect
my father, the Emperor,

126
00:10:00,499 --> 00:10:02,768
and come to the Emperor's aid.

127
00:10:11,410 --> 00:10:12,410
Hiya!

128
00:10:24,490 --> 00:10:26,192
Now I finally understand your plan.

129
00:10:27,493 --> 00:10:29,573
You deliberately let Yin
Zhou and Su He join forces.

130
00:10:30,329 --> 00:10:31,964
When their ambitions are exposed,

131
00:10:32,365 --> 00:10:33,542
you can kill two birds with one stone,

132
00:10:33,566 --> 00:10:34,967
using my father to eliminate them.

133
00:10:36,535 --> 00:10:37,535
But Yanzhi,

134
00:10:38,638 --> 00:10:40,773
your plan has failed.

135
00:10:41,707 --> 00:10:42,975
They even deceived you.

136
00:10:43,442 --> 00:10:44,977
A Qi,

137
00:10:46,379 --> 00:10:47,480
why are you so sure?

138
00:10:48,714 --> 00:10:49,714
Yanzhi...

139
00:10:51,183 --> 00:10:52,184
Do you trust me?

140
00:10:53,185 --> 00:10:54,253
Of course I trust you.

141
00:10:56,088 --> 00:10:57,556
Since Concubine Chen's death,

142
00:10:58,057 --> 00:10:59,497
you've been like a different person.

143
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,700
You can see through everything I do.

144
00:11:04,397 --> 00:11:05,397
You ask me

145
00:11:05,898 --> 00:11:07,266
why I'm so sure you'll fail.

146
00:11:07,967 --> 00:11:08,967
Because

147
00:11:10,036 --> 00:11:11,537
we've already died once.

148
00:11:16,442 --> 00:11:19,078
In my previous life, I went to the border.

149
00:11:19,912 --> 00:11:21,414
You carried out your plan.

150
00:11:21,981 --> 00:11:23,182
In three years,

151
00:11:23,582 --> 00:11:25,484
Yin Zhou and Su He planned everything.

152
00:11:26,352 --> 00:11:27,620
They made me believe

153
00:11:28,187 --> 00:11:29,822
that you were a spy sent by Talhan.

154
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:32,910
They plotted to make me
return to the Central Plains.

155
00:11:33,259 --> 00:11:35,861
I mistakenly thought you had killed my
father, the Emperor. So I turned against you.

156
00:11:37,129 --> 00:11:40,250
That battle was extremely fierce.

157
00:11:44,570 --> 00:11:48,040
In the end, we both died
under Yin Zhou's sword.

158
00:11:49,141 --> 00:11:50,409
When I woke up again,

159
00:11:51,177 --> 00:11:52,411
I had returned three years in the past,

160
00:11:53,712 --> 00:11:55,414
the day before my mother's death.

161
00:11:57,049 --> 00:11:58,884
A Qi,

162
00:12:02,121 --> 00:12:03,641
if you want to persuade me to give up,

163
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:05,190
there's no need to

164
00:12:06,058 --> 00:12:07,860
make up such a bizarre story to deceive me.

165
00:12:08,661 --> 00:12:10,930
I know it's hard to believe,

166
00:12:11,363 --> 00:12:12,465
but it's true.

167
00:12:18,571 --> 00:12:19,571
Let me ask you,

168
00:12:20,306 --> 00:12:21,306
Su He,

169
00:12:22,174 --> 00:12:23,642
does the left cheek of his confidant

170
00:12:24,543 --> 00:12:25,778
have a scar?

171
00:12:27,179 --> 00:12:29,224
In my previous life,
during the battle at the imperial villa,

172
00:12:29,248 --> 00:12:30,248
I saw him.

173
00:12:33,886 --> 00:12:35,955
Pei Yanzhi, you traitor!

174
00:12:37,189 --> 00:12:38,189
A Qi,

175
00:12:38,357 --> 00:12:39,225
You're delirious from illness.

176
00:12:39,258 --> 00:12:41,418
Your son has a request to
seek the Emperor's approval.

177
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:42,228
Before Mother passed away,

178
00:12:42,261 --> 00:12:43,261
Heshu, shut up!

179
00:12:56,175 --> 00:12:56,842
A Qi,

180
00:12:56,942 --> 00:12:58,611
What on earth are you trying to do, A Qi?

181
00:12:58,911 --> 00:13:00,589
Rather than let you go
down an irreversible path,

182
00:13:00,613 --> 00:13:01,247
it's better to

183
00:13:01,447 --> 00:13:02,967
keep you in Yunhe Palace all the time.

184
00:13:05,417 --> 00:13:06,417
No wonder

185
00:13:09,088 --> 00:13:10,198
you planned everything so early on,

186
00:13:10,222 --> 00:13:12,124
how to send Concubine
Chen back to Jiangnan,

187
00:13:12,691 --> 00:13:13,691
and also planned

188
00:13:14,093 --> 00:13:15,973
how to make the Emperor
keep you in the palace,

189
00:13:16,228 --> 00:13:18,063
and even gradually
gain the Emperor's trust.

190
00:13:19,098 --> 00:13:20,099
So,

191
00:13:22,134 --> 00:13:23,435
the rumors in the palace

192
00:13:23,861 --> 00:13:25,262
about you becoming the Crown Prince

193
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:27,458
were also spread by you yourself.

194
00:13:28,407 --> 00:13:29,567
You wanted to alarm Yin Zhou.

195
00:13:31,677 --> 00:13:32,677
Yanzhi,

196
00:13:33,078 --> 00:13:34,380
Don't you understand yet?

197
00:13:34,813 --> 00:13:35,881
To deal with them,

198
00:13:36,248 --> 00:13:37,282
relying solely on you won't work,

199
00:13:37,283 --> 00:13:38,483
nor will relying solely on me.

200
00:13:39,051 --> 00:13:41,353
We must unite to have a chance of winning.

201
00:13:54,934 --> 00:13:55,934
Does it hurt?

202
00:14:04,243 --> 00:14:05,243
I'm sorry.

203
00:14:08,447 --> 00:14:09,447
But

204
00:14:09,849 --> 00:14:11,250
why was it only you that was reborn?

205
00:14:21,427 --> 00:14:22,587
I think it's because of this.

206
00:14:23,729 --> 00:14:24,729
Before I died,

207
00:14:24,964 --> 00:14:28,067
I was clutching this
wolf's tooth in my hand.

208
00:14:32,004 --> 00:14:33,004
So,

209
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:36,709
what the White-Eyed Wolf King
told me in my dream was all true.

210
00:15:04,036 --> 00:15:05,237
Yanzhi, stop!

211
00:15:06,906 --> 00:15:09,174
Why won't you let me touch
your wolf's tooth pendant?

212
00:15:09,608 --> 00:15:13,722
This is a token that the White-Eyed
Wolf King asked me to give to my beloved.

213
00:15:13,746 --> 00:15:14,880
It can bless the two lovers

214
00:15:15,281 --> 00:15:16,749
to be together for all eternity.

215
00:15:19,318 --> 00:15:20,318
How is that possible?

216
00:15:21,487 --> 00:15:22,487
Do you remember

217
00:15:22,688 --> 00:15:24,368
when I first arrived at the Daxing palace,

218
00:15:24,544 --> 00:15:25,544
the people in the palace

219
00:15:25,847 --> 00:15:27,687
all said I was a barbarian
from the grasslands

220
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,638
because I had killed the
White-Eyed Wolf King,

221
00:15:29,662 --> 00:15:31,142
and took the opportunity to bully me.

222
00:15:33,899 --> 00:15:35,434
Actually, I didn't kill the Wolf King.

223
00:15:35,901 --> 00:15:37,736
On the contrary, I once saved him

224
00:15:38,904 --> 00:15:39,904
and treated his wounds.

225
00:15:40,239 --> 00:15:41,239
Then one day,

226
00:15:41,540 --> 00:15:43,575
he placed this wolf's tooth beside me.

227
00:15:44,276 --> 00:15:45,878
That night, he told me in a dream

228
00:15:46,111 --> 00:15:46,645
What?

229
00:15:47,079 --> 00:15:49,214
He said he was the messenger
of the God of Longevity,

230
00:15:49,682 --> 00:15:51,162
and in gratitude for saving his life,

231
00:15:51,650 --> 00:15:53,652
he asked me to wear this wolf's tooth,

232
00:15:54,453 --> 00:15:55,653
and when one day in the future

233
00:15:57,656 --> 00:15:58,691
I met the person I loved,

234
00:16:01,727 --> 00:16:02,727
it would bless us

235
00:16:04,430 --> 00:16:06,565
to be destined lovers for all eternity.

236
00:16:12,438 --> 00:16:13,438
Yes,

237
00:16:14,073 --> 00:16:16,073
everything the White-Eyed
Wolf King said was true.

238
00:16:20,990 --> 00:16:22,892
You ask me why I always interfere with you.

239
00:16:23,849 --> 00:16:25,985
Even though I know the
outcome will be so tragic,

240
00:16:27,252 --> 00:16:28,654
shouldn't I try to stop it?

241
00:16:30,622 --> 00:16:31,622
A Qi,

242
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:33,358
You've told me everything

243
00:16:33,359 --> 00:16:34,799
that happened in your previous life.

244
00:16:35,361 --> 00:16:36,695
We can take the initiative.

245
00:16:37,663 --> 00:16:38,663
In this life,

246
00:16:39,298 --> 00:16:40,466
I will definitely save you.

247
00:16:40,966 --> 00:16:41,966
It's us.

248
00:16:43,035 --> 00:16:44,103
We must both survive.

249
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,138
Now, the Crown Prince

250
00:16:46,905 --> 00:16:48,507
thinks we've completely split up.

251
00:16:49,008 --> 00:16:50,008
Why don't we

252
00:16:50,109 --> 00:16:51,243
play along with his plan

253
00:16:52,010 --> 00:16:53,010
and make him think

254
00:16:53,846 --> 00:16:55,547
that I've lost your support,

255
00:16:57,816 --> 00:16:59,084
making him let down his guard

256
00:16:59,651 --> 00:17:00,731
and reveal his true colors?

257
00:17:05,624 --> 00:17:06,624
You've worked hard.

258
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:22,940
Your Highness.

259
00:17:23,342 --> 00:17:25,344
I met with my uncle at Yanbo Tower.

260
00:17:26,345 --> 00:17:28,414
He was eager to help Your Highness.

261
00:17:29,314 --> 00:17:30,716
But for some reason,

262
00:17:31,051 --> 00:17:32,851
Your Highness suddenly
broke the appointment.

263
00:17:33,619 --> 00:17:34,619
It seems

264
00:17:34,642 --> 00:17:36,802
that Your Highness doesn't
want to ally with my uncle.

265
00:17:40,260 --> 00:17:42,095
Your uncle wants to help me,

266
00:17:42,728 --> 00:17:45,455
of course, he wants to
gain something from me.

267
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:47,284
Since that's the case,

268
00:17:48,446 --> 00:17:50,381
I naturally have to consider it carefully.

269
00:17:53,105 --> 00:17:54,540
I came to tell Your Highness

270
00:17:55,140 --> 00:17:57,042
that my uncle will soon leave Jiangnan.

271
00:17:57,910 --> 00:17:59,710
Your Highness can take
your time to consider.

272
00:17:59,878 --> 00:18:00,878
Wait.

273
00:18:05,617 --> 00:18:06,617
You and Yin Qi

274
00:18:07,014 --> 00:18:08,682
have become estranged so quickly?

275
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:15,799
From the moment I decided
to work for Your Highness

276
00:18:15,822 --> 00:18:17,090
and win over my uncle,

277
00:18:18,030 --> 00:18:19,030
A Qi and I

278
00:18:20,165 --> 00:18:21,685
were destined to go our separate ways.

279
00:18:29,107 --> 00:18:30,876
To save Yin Qi's life,

280
00:18:31,810 --> 00:18:33,345
making you turn against each other,

281
00:18:35,013 --> 00:18:36,748
Pei Yanzhi, Pei Yanzhi,

282
00:18:37,282 --> 00:18:38,550
even I

283
00:18:39,685 --> 00:18:41,386
can't help but feel sorry for you.

284
00:18:48,026 --> 00:18:48,694
Your Highness,

285
00:18:49,027 --> 00:18:51,429
Su He has assembled a
team of grassland warriors

286
00:18:51,430 --> 00:18:52,430
for your disposal.

287
00:18:52,998 --> 00:18:54,766
They have secretly entered the city today.

288
00:18:55,467 --> 00:18:57,669
I've had them hide in the south of the city

289
00:18:58,036 --> 00:18:59,638
to avoid drawing attention.

290
00:19:01,513 --> 00:19:05,205
I know exactly how many
troops are in the imperial villa.

291
00:19:06,346 --> 00:19:11,049
With Su He's men,
victory is within my grasp.

292
00:19:11,950 --> 00:19:14,153
After all, Su He is a foreigner.

293
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:15,720
Can he be trusted?

294
00:19:16,622 --> 00:19:18,857
Su He and Pei Yanzhi are
cut from the same cloth.

295
00:19:19,791 --> 00:19:21,425
He won't miss out

296
00:19:21,426 --> 00:19:22,528
on anything profitable.

297
00:19:23,862 --> 00:19:24,862
Moreover,

298
00:19:25,430 --> 00:19:26,899
he understands better than anyone

299
00:19:27,633 --> 00:19:29,301
that once he's on my boat,

300
00:19:29,501 --> 00:19:30,936
if he gives up halfway,

301
00:19:33,639 --> 00:19:34,940
I won't spare him.

302
00:19:36,441 --> 00:19:37,681
Congratulations, Your Highness.

303
00:19:38,076 --> 00:19:41,180
You'll soon get what you want.

304
00:20:05,837 --> 00:20:06,837
What did you feed me?

305
00:20:10,008 --> 00:20:11,610
To make me believe you,

306
00:20:12,557 --> 00:20:13,692
you naturally have to show

307
00:20:14,479 --> 00:20:16,515
a willingness to be used by me.

308
00:20:20,485 --> 00:20:21,485
Don't worry,

309
00:20:22,221 --> 00:20:24,623
this poison won't cause you much pain.

310
00:20:25,524 --> 00:20:27,484
As long as you come for
the antidote every month,

311
00:20:28,305 --> 00:20:31,876
I'll ensure your safety.

312
00:20:35,701 --> 00:20:37,035
Every time I see your eyes,

313
00:20:37,069 --> 00:20:38,669
I can't help but want to gouge them out.

314
00:20:54,252 --> 00:20:55,354
Your Highness is joking.

315
00:20:57,155 --> 00:20:58,557
If I didn't have eyes,

316
00:20:59,625 --> 00:21:01,025
how could I work for Your Highness?

317
00:21:03,247 --> 00:21:06,560
Don't think that I really believe
the words of a foreigner like you.

318
00:21:07,305 --> 00:21:09,907
If you want to live and
protect your Fifth Prince,

319
00:21:10,809 --> 00:21:12,845
you'd better obey me obediently.

320
00:21:14,473 --> 00:21:16,008
If you dare to betray me,

321
00:21:19,347 --> 00:21:20,815
I'll make you know

322
00:21:21,736 --> 00:21:22,937
what it means

323
00:21:24,249 --> 00:21:25,284
to be torn apart.

324
00:21:28,687 --> 00:21:30,088
This poison is really strange.

325
00:21:31,223 --> 00:21:33,143
I can't expel it even
with my internal strength.

326
00:21:33,358 --> 00:21:34,760
I can only delay its onset.

327
00:21:39,765 --> 00:21:40,765
Yanzhi.

328
00:21:41,366 --> 00:21:42,366
Yanzhi.

329
00:21:49,207 --> 00:21:50,847
Didn't I tell you to be careful recently?

330
00:21:51,076 --> 00:21:52,396
Why are you looking for me again?

331
00:21:52,844 --> 00:21:53,712
I've been very careful.

332
00:21:53,712 --> 00:21:54,712
No one has noticed.

333
00:21:55,514 --> 00:21:56,514
Don't worry.

334
00:21:57,549 --> 00:21:58,650
Come to think of it,

335
00:21:59,631 --> 00:22:01,933
we haven't taken a bath
together for many years.

336
00:22:02,721 --> 00:22:06,009
The last time was during the autumn hunt,
when we bathed in the river together, no?

337
00:22:07,626 --> 00:22:08,894
In my memory,

338
00:22:09,561 --> 00:22:11,596
I guarded the border alone for three years.

339
00:22:15,233 --> 00:22:16,233
At that time,

340
00:22:17,102 --> 00:22:18,470
didn't I stop you?

341
00:22:20,405 --> 00:22:22,874
We had a big fight over it.

342
00:22:24,710 --> 00:22:25,977
For three years,

343
00:22:26,845 --> 00:22:28,325
neither of us was willing to give in.

344
00:22:28,714 --> 00:22:32,617
Even through letters, we didn't
even want to hear about each other.

345
00:22:42,227 --> 00:22:43,495
But all that is in the past.

346
00:22:44,229 --> 00:22:45,669
You don't have to feel sorry for me.

347
00:22:45,831 --> 00:22:47,132
I'm fine now, aren't I?

348
00:22:51,470 --> 00:22:52,470
You are fine.

349
00:22:53,004 --> 00:22:54,844
Even though you are
three years older than me.

350
00:22:55,307 --> 00:22:56,307
What?

351
00:22:56,408 --> 00:22:57,408
Don't you believe it?

352
00:22:58,076 --> 00:22:59,076
I do.

353
00:23:00,312 --> 00:23:01,312
I just think

354
00:23:02,147 --> 00:23:05,095
being alone at the border for three years,

355
00:23:05,684 --> 00:23:07,124
it must not have been easy.

356
00:23:16,194 --> 00:23:17,262
Recently, I suddenly found

357
00:23:18,096 --> 00:23:20,232
that for some unknown reason,

358
00:23:20,465 --> 00:23:21,705
there's a red mark on my chest.

359
00:23:22,968 --> 00:23:24,770
It's in exactly the same spot.

360
00:23:29,441 --> 00:23:30,441
In our past life,

361
00:23:30,909 --> 00:23:31,910
it was right here

362
00:23:31,943 --> 00:23:33,063
that we were shot by arrows.

363
00:23:35,347 --> 00:23:36,381
So it was here.

364
00:23:40,652 --> 00:23:42,454
We've changed so many things.

365
00:23:43,155 --> 00:23:45,891
We will definitely survive this life.

366
00:23:47,359 --> 00:23:48,359
Yanzhi.

367
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,780
We won't let go of
each other's hands again

368
00:23:51,563 --> 00:23:52,563
Right?

369
00:23:53,698 --> 00:23:56,310
Although I don't have memories
of those three years in our past life,

370
00:23:56,334 --> 00:23:57,854
but whether it was me in the past life

371
00:23:57,969 --> 00:23:59,037
or me in this life,

372
00:23:59,671 --> 00:24:00,671
my feelings for you

373
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:02,440
have never changed.

374
00:24:04,943 --> 00:24:06,845
I came back to this life

375
00:24:07,712 --> 00:24:09,214
just to make sure we survive

376
00:24:10,048 --> 00:24:11,048
and stay together.

377
00:24:11,616 --> 00:24:12,616
Survive.

378
00:24:14,519 --> 00:24:15,519
What's wrong?

379
00:24:16,354 --> 00:24:17,354
Are you cold?

380
00:24:20,392 --> 00:24:21,392
A Qi.

381
00:24:23,028 --> 00:24:25,508
I may only be able to accompany you
for a little while longer.

382
00:24:26,932 --> 00:24:28,600
You have to live well for me.

383
00:24:29,801 --> 00:24:30,801
Live as

384
00:24:31,503 --> 00:24:32,804
the free and fearless Yin Qi.

385
00:24:54,626 --> 00:24:55,627
In my humble opinion,

386
00:24:56,261 --> 00:24:57,821
when Su He comes to Jiangnan this time,

387
00:24:58,623 --> 00:25:00,583
he will definitely try his
best to meet with Yin Zhou.

388
00:25:02,100 --> 00:25:03,100
Given his personality,

389
00:25:03,835 --> 00:25:04,995
if there's something to gain,

390
00:25:05,604 --> 00:25:06,905
he won't give up easily.

391
00:25:09,841 --> 00:25:12,844
Has Yin Zhou made any moves recently?

392
00:25:13,912 --> 00:25:15,313
He's been very quiet lately.

393
00:25:15,847 --> 00:25:17,607
He's been accompanying
the emperor on trips.

394
00:25:17,716 --> 00:25:18,716
And in his free time,

395
00:25:18,917 --> 00:25:20,018
he stays in his palace.

396
00:25:21,653 --> 00:25:22,854
But in my opinion,

397
00:25:23,521 --> 00:25:24,623
his calmness

398
00:25:25,223 --> 00:25:26,583
must mean he's planning something.

399
00:25:31,229 --> 00:25:33,665
Your uncle hasn't left Jiangnan City.

400
00:25:34,099 --> 00:25:36,835
He's also sent a group of
grassland warriors to Jiangnan.

401
00:25:38,236 --> 00:25:40,156
They're hiding in the
southern part of the city.

402
00:25:40,605 --> 00:25:41,605
I don't know

403
00:25:41,673 --> 00:25:43,275
what he's up to.

404
00:25:43,875 --> 00:25:44,995
According to what A Qi said,

405
00:25:45,644 --> 00:25:47,077
Yin Zhou and Su He will

406
00:25:47,078 --> 00:25:48,278
rebel together in three years.

407
00:25:49,481 --> 00:25:51,401
Now, because of Yin
Qi's presence as a variable,

408
00:25:51,883 --> 00:25:53,643
are they planning to
move up their schedule?

409
00:25:54,953 --> 00:25:55,287
Senior,

410
00:25:55,887 --> 00:25:56,887
I have a favor to ask.

411
00:25:57,822 --> 00:26:00,158
As long as you don't tear
down my Jiangnan City,

412
00:26:00,625 --> 00:26:01,826
just ask.

413
00:26:02,494 --> 00:26:03,494
I'm afraid

414
00:26:04,462 --> 00:26:05,864
it's not me

415
00:26:06,264 --> 00:26:07,744
who wants to tear down Jiangnan City,

416
00:26:07,866 --> 00:26:09,000
but Su He and Yin Zhou.

417
00:26:12,137 --> 00:26:15,574
Although Yin Zhou is ruthless,

418
00:26:16,474 --> 00:26:18,743
rebelling is a serious crime.

419
00:26:19,945 --> 00:26:22,681
Does he really have the guts?

420
00:26:23,348 --> 00:26:26,251
Now, Yin Zhou's position is delicate.

421
00:26:27,652 --> 00:26:28,652
In the court,

422
00:26:28,853 --> 00:26:31,198
he and the imperial uncle have
gradually lost the emperor's trust.

423
00:26:31,222 --> 00:26:32,982
The queen is also not
favored in the palace.

424
00:26:33,558 --> 00:26:34,793
If it weren't for Su He,

425
00:26:36,528 --> 00:26:37,929
he might still be hesitating.

426
00:26:38,863 --> 00:26:39,863
But now,

427
00:26:40,832 --> 00:26:42,233
with Su He's full support,

428
00:26:42,534 --> 00:26:45,170
it's very likely he'll take the plunge.

429
00:26:49,007 --> 00:26:50,508
Given this,

430
00:26:51,142 --> 00:26:53,878
it's indeed a good opportunity
for him to rebel now.

431
00:26:57,816 --> 00:26:59,084
What do you need me to do?

432
00:26:59,250 --> 00:27:00,250
Just tell me.

433
00:27:00,518 --> 00:27:02,454
Why do I keep running into you everywhere?

434
00:27:02,921 --> 00:27:04,222
The person I'm looking for today

435
00:27:04,255 --> 00:27:05,357
is your boss.

436
00:27:05,924 --> 00:27:07,025
Where is your boss?

437
00:27:07,492 --> 00:27:08,827
My boss of Yanbo Tower

438
00:27:08,860 --> 00:27:10,805
isn't someone you can
just see whenever you want.

439
00:27:10,829 --> 00:27:11,896
To see her,

440
00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:13,370
you have to tell me your name first.

441
00:27:15,266 --> 00:27:16,666
I have important business with her.

442
00:27:16,835 --> 00:27:17,955
How much silver do you want?

443
00:27:18,036 --> 00:27:19,036
I'll give it to you.

444
00:27:19,437 --> 00:27:20,939
Just tell her

445
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:22,740
that

446
00:27:23,842 --> 00:27:25,282
I have business to discuss with her.

447
00:27:25,610 --> 00:27:27,112
My Lin family of Jiangnan

448
00:27:27,145 --> 00:27:28,545
wouldn't lack your little business.

449
00:27:30,150 --> 00:27:32,550
I'm not going to waste my breath with you.
I'll go in and find her myself.

450
00:27:37,489 --> 00:27:38,489
Brother Yanzhi.

451
00:27:39,624 --> 00:27:40,725
Please help me speak up.

452
00:27:40,825 --> 00:27:42,145
I want to go in and see the boss.

453
00:27:43,111 --> 00:27:44,111
Excuse me.

454
00:27:44,696 --> 00:27:45,530
Come back with me quickly.

455
00:27:45,663 --> 00:27:46,823
Don't let your brother worry.

456
00:27:46,931 --> 00:27:47,931
I'm not going back.

457
00:27:48,433 --> 00:27:49,467
I want to know about my

458
00:27:50,101 --> 00:27:51,101
mother.

459
00:27:51,302 --> 00:27:53,271
Who in this huge Jiangnan City knows me?

460
00:27:53,471 --> 00:27:54,615
I'll just stroll out confidently.

461
00:27:54,639 --> 00:27:56,199
What danger could I possibly encounter?

462
00:28:14,626 --> 00:28:15,626
Aunt.

463
00:28:15,649 --> 00:28:17,889
There have been many
foreigners on the streets recently.

464
00:28:18,329 --> 00:28:20,065
Could they be targeting them?

465
00:28:23,334 --> 00:28:24,469
Heshu, slow down.

466
00:28:27,439 --> 00:28:28,373
Good nephew.

467
00:28:28,406 --> 00:28:29,340
Don't be in such a hurry to leave.

468
00:28:29,341 --> 00:28:31,142
Stop eating and let's go.

469
00:28:32,877 --> 00:28:33,877
Uncle.

470
00:28:38,717 --> 00:28:39,717
Uncle.

471
00:28:41,086 --> 00:28:42,086
What is the meaning of this?

472
00:28:42,253 --> 00:28:45,290
I heard your elder brother
gave you the military talisman.

473
00:28:46,124 --> 00:28:47,792
Such an important item

474
00:28:47,926 --> 00:28:50,995
might not be safe with a hostage.

475
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:54,132
Why not let your uncle keep it for you?

476
00:28:55,366 --> 00:28:56,366
Su He.

477
00:28:56,768 --> 00:28:58,937
Your treacherous ambitions
can no longer be hidden.

478
00:28:59,237 --> 00:29:00,671
Such an important military talisman

479
00:29:00,672 --> 00:29:01,272
how could it be entrusted to you?

480
00:29:01,273 --> 00:29:02,607
It's not your turn to speak.

481
00:29:05,410 --> 00:29:06,410
Fengsun.

482
00:29:07,245 --> 00:29:09,445
Out of consideration for our
uncle-nephew relationship,

483
00:29:09,647 --> 00:29:10,647
today,

484
00:29:10,782 --> 00:29:12,359
if you hand over the
military talisman obediently,

485
00:29:12,383 --> 00:29:13,383
I, the Khan,

486
00:29:13,918 --> 00:29:15,320
can spare your life.

487
00:29:15,754 --> 00:29:16,754
If you

488
00:29:17,088 --> 00:29:18,088
remain obstinate,

489
00:29:18,523 --> 00:29:19,924
then don't blame your uncle

490
00:29:20,191 --> 00:29:21,526
for turning my back on you.

491
00:29:24,129 --> 00:29:25,730
Uncle once promised Father Khan

492
00:29:27,065 --> 00:29:28,532
to send your own son

493
00:29:28,533 --> 00:29:29,834
to Daxing as a hostage.

494
00:29:30,835 --> 00:29:33,481
A few days ago, you also tricked me
by saying you wanted to return to Talhan.

495
00:29:33,505 --> 00:29:35,916
It seems Uncle is even more fickle
than the Central Plains people.

496
00:29:35,940 --> 00:29:36,940
You...

497
00:29:41,846 --> 00:29:42,846
I knew it.

498
00:29:44,215 --> 00:29:45,215
All along,

499
00:29:45,517 --> 00:29:46,751
your humble demeanor

500
00:29:47,118 --> 00:29:48,953
was just an act.

501
00:29:50,114 --> 00:29:50,681
Today,

502
00:29:51,122 --> 00:29:52,957
I'll tell you the truth.

503
00:29:53,958 --> 00:29:55,193
For the past ten years,

504
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:58,855
I've wanted to kill you every moment
to eliminate future troubles.

505
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:00,430
Today,

506
00:30:00,832 --> 00:30:03,668
I finally have the
chance to take your life.

507
00:30:04,536 --> 00:30:05,136
Attack!

508
00:30:05,370 --> 00:30:06,370
Wait!

509
00:30:16,014 --> 00:30:17,048
You, guest,

510
00:30:17,715 --> 00:30:19,450
this is Jiangnan territory.

511
00:30:20,552 --> 00:30:22,821
If you really smash my Yanbo Tower,

512
00:30:23,721 --> 00:30:25,723
I'm afraid you can't afford to compensate.

513
00:30:29,260 --> 00:30:30,562
You, the boss lady,

514
00:30:30,929 --> 00:30:32,130
have quite a big mouth.

515
00:30:33,031 --> 00:30:34,399
It's just a tavern.

516
00:30:34,966 --> 00:30:36,134
Do you think our Khan

517
00:30:36,768 --> 00:30:37,768
is afraid of you?

518
00:30:44,843 --> 00:30:46,678
We have a saying in the Central Plains,

519
00:30:47,011 --> 00:30:49,480
"Even a mighty dragon
doesn't bully the local snake."

520
00:30:50,682 --> 00:30:52,584
Although I'm just a woman,

521
00:30:53,251 --> 00:30:54,886
in Jiangnan,

522
00:30:55,453 --> 00:30:58,556
no one dares to disrespect Lin Jianshuang.

523
00:31:01,359 --> 00:31:02,359
Lin Jianshuang.

524
00:31:03,649 --> 00:31:05,084
What's your relationship

525
00:31:06,931 --> 00:31:08,211
with the Lin family of Jiangnan?

526
00:31:08,686 --> 00:31:11,022
The head of the Lin family
of Jiangnan is my aunt.

527
00:31:15,340 --> 00:31:16,340
Khan.

528
00:31:16,981 --> 00:31:19,296
Your subordinate didn't know
she was Boss Lin.

529
00:31:31,122 --> 00:31:32,122
Fengsun.

530
00:31:33,491 --> 00:31:34,893
You can hide for a while,

531
00:31:35,426 --> 00:31:36,461
but not forever.

532
00:31:37,662 --> 00:31:38,896
What belongs to me, the Khan,

533
00:31:39,097 --> 00:31:41,991
I will take it back
sooner or later.

534
00:31:45,737 --> 00:31:46,737
Let's go.

535
00:31:56,347 --> 00:31:57,347
A Qi.

536
00:31:58,416 --> 00:31:59,416
Why are you here?

537
00:31:59,784 --> 00:32:01,319
The senior sent someone to fetch me.

538
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,254
I just found out

539
00:32:04,088 --> 00:32:05,423
that Su He, in broad daylight,

540
00:32:05,523 --> 00:32:07,125
actually fought with you in the city.

541
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:09,960
Are you

542
00:32:10,228 --> 00:32:11,296
hurt?

543
00:32:12,363 --> 00:32:13,363
Sit down and talk.

544
00:32:20,705 --> 00:32:21,705
Today,

545
00:32:22,006 --> 00:32:24,642
thank you, senior, for
saving my sister and Yanzhi.

546
00:32:25,610 --> 00:32:26,610
I didn't expect

547
00:32:26,878 --> 00:32:28,880
Yanzhi has such a connection with you.

548
00:32:29,914 --> 00:32:30,515
However,

549
00:32:30,715 --> 00:32:31,795
please forgive my boldness,

550
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:34,986
may I ask who you really are?

551
00:32:37,622 --> 00:32:39,557
My aunt kindly saved your sister,

552
00:32:39,657 --> 00:32:41,035
Not only do you fail to appreciate her,

553
00:32:41,059 --> 00:32:42,299
yet you question her like this.

554
00:32:42,627 --> 00:32:43,827
Do you think it's appropriate?

555
00:32:44,228 --> 00:32:45,930
Although Brother Yanzhi trusts you,

556
00:32:46,331 --> 00:32:47,564
we should still ask clearly

557
00:32:47,565 --> 00:32:48,800
what your intentions are.

558
00:32:48,936 --> 00:32:49,477
You...

559
00:32:51,302 --> 00:32:52,302
May I ask, senior,

560
00:32:53,071 --> 00:32:54,539
do you know my mother?

561
00:32:55,306 --> 00:32:56,306
My mother

562
00:32:56,874 --> 00:32:58,142
is the Imperial Concubine Chen.

563
00:32:59,277 --> 00:33:01,837
The most beautiful woman in Jiangnan
you mentioned the other day

564
00:33:01,879 --> 00:33:02,879
is her.

565
00:33:23,368 --> 00:33:24,368
This handkerchief...

566
00:33:24,702 --> 00:33:25,702
It's...

567
00:33:27,438 --> 00:33:28,438
That's right.

568
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:30,040
Your mother

569
00:33:30,508 --> 00:33:32,310
was my dear friend in my youth.

570
00:33:34,011 --> 00:33:35,079
Back then, she

571
00:33:36,114 --> 00:33:37,274
wasn't called Concubine Chen.

572
00:33:39,283 --> 00:33:40,283
She was called

573
00:33:41,252 --> 00:33:42,754
Su Tang'er.

574
00:33:44,322 --> 00:33:45,322
Tang'er.

575
00:33:46,024 --> 00:33:47,258
I stitched this myself.

576
00:33:47,558 --> 00:33:48,558
For you.

577
00:33:48,960 --> 00:33:50,228
You stitched it so beautifully.

578
00:33:50,695 --> 00:33:51,895
I didn't expect you, who's
busy with business every day,

579
00:33:51,896 --> 00:33:52,896
to have such skills.

580
00:33:54,265 --> 00:33:55,265
By the way,

581
00:33:55,366 --> 00:33:58,336
It seems Miss Liu from
West Street is getting married.

582
00:33:58,770 --> 00:33:59,890
I wonder what kind of person

583
00:34:00,138 --> 00:34:01,339
you'll marry in the future.

584
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:05,120
After marriage, you have to
take care of your husband and children.

585
00:34:05,243 --> 00:34:06,377
I don't want to get married.

586
00:34:06,878 --> 00:34:08,638
I want to be a female
warrior in the future.

587
00:34:09,213 --> 00:34:10,493
Being a female warrior is great.

588
00:34:10,681 --> 00:34:11,949
My father found me a master

589
00:34:12,116 --> 00:34:12,817
to teach me martial arts.

590
00:34:13,017 --> 00:34:13,751
After I learn it,

591
00:34:13,951 --> 00:34:14,352
I'll teach you.

592
00:34:14,719 --> 00:34:16,821
Okay, then teach me now.

593
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:29,199
Come on.

594
00:34:29,567 --> 00:34:31,636
Look, your hair is all messy.

595
00:34:33,805 --> 00:34:34,805
Okay.

596
00:34:35,139 --> 00:34:36,407
Back then, Tang'er

597
00:34:36,524 --> 00:34:37,158
So ticklish!

598
00:34:37,208 --> 00:34:40,545
She was the happiest and most
carefree person in the world.

599
00:34:40,812 --> 00:34:41,512
Slow down.

600
00:34:41,646 --> 00:34:42,547
I thought we

601
00:34:42,548 --> 00:34:43,748
would be best friends forever.

602
00:34:45,249 --> 00:34:46,551
Until that day.

603
00:34:59,897 --> 00:35:02,097
If we're talking about the
most scenic place in Daxing,

604
00:35:02,567 --> 00:35:05,002
Jiangnan with its misty rain tops the list.

605
00:35:05,570 --> 00:35:06,850
Although Jiangnan City is small,

606
00:35:07,205 --> 00:35:08,339
it's quite exquisite.

607
00:35:09,073 --> 00:35:10,507
Although the capital is prosperous,

608
00:35:10,508 --> 00:35:13,262
you can't see the scenery of
small bridges and flowing water.

609
00:35:13,811 --> 00:35:15,111
It's all thanks to His Majesty's wisdom

610
00:35:15,112 --> 00:35:16,380
and capable governance

611
00:35:16,414 --> 00:35:18,854
that the people of Jiangnan can
live in peace and prosperity.

612
00:36:07,031 --> 00:36:08,031
Tang'er.

613
00:36:10,935 --> 00:36:12,375
Take care of yourself in the future.

614
00:36:15,239 --> 00:36:16,239
Not long after,

615
00:36:16,641 --> 00:36:19,243
news came that she was to
enter the palace as a concubine.

616
00:36:20,611 --> 00:36:21,479
I knew in her heart,

617
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:23,681
she was actually unwilling.

618
00:36:25,016 --> 00:36:26,249
But how could she possibly

619
00:36:26,250 --> 00:36:28,090
make decisions based
solely on her own wishes?

620
00:36:30,154 --> 00:36:31,188
From that day on,

621
00:36:31,956 --> 00:36:33,758
we were separated by a great distance,

622
00:36:34,091 --> 00:36:35,611
and never heard from each other again.

623
00:36:37,228 --> 00:36:40,498
I used to be with my mother day and night,

624
00:36:41,465 --> 00:36:42,767
yet I never knew

625
00:36:43,634 --> 00:36:45,794
what my mother was like
before she entered the palace.

626
00:36:46,837 --> 00:36:47,837
No wonder

627
00:36:48,573 --> 00:36:49,707
before she left,

628
00:36:50,341 --> 00:36:52,677
she yearned to return to Jiangnan.

629
00:36:53,844 --> 00:36:55,947
If only my mother had
never entered the palace.

630
00:36:56,547 --> 00:36:57,547
She would surely

631
00:36:57,815 --> 00:36:59,417
be very happy now.

632
00:37:01,719 --> 00:37:02,719
My aunt never revealed

633
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:04,722
her identity to you before

634
00:37:05,089 --> 00:37:06,833
firstly, because she was afraid the
emperor would be suspicious,

635
00:37:06,857 --> 00:37:08,657
and secondly, to prevent
any unexpected problems.

636
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,094
Actually, all along the way,

637
00:37:10,228 --> 00:37:10,962
we've been

638
00:37:10,963 --> 00:37:12,563
secretly protecting you and your sister.

639
00:37:14,165 --> 00:37:15,165
I didn't expect

640
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,000
that you and our mother

641
00:37:17,235 --> 00:37:18,636
had such a connection.

642
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:23,760
After Tang'er entered the palace,

643
00:37:24,342 --> 00:37:27,144
I tried every means to
find out how she was doing.

644
00:37:28,879 --> 00:37:29,879
I heard

645
00:37:30,348 --> 00:37:31,515
she was very favored

646
00:37:32,617 --> 00:37:34,057
and even became a beloved concubine.

647
00:37:34,919 --> 00:37:35,920
Then I was relieved.

648
00:37:40,891 --> 00:37:41,891
But

649
00:37:42,426 --> 00:37:45,899
too many people knew about her past,

650
00:37:45,923 --> 00:37:47,858
which might not have good for her.

651
00:37:49,367 --> 00:37:50,668
Fate is truly cruel.

652
00:37:54,005 --> 00:37:55,339
For so many years,

653
00:37:56,273 --> 00:37:58,342
I've always wanted to see her again.

654
00:38:00,678 --> 00:38:01,679
Who would have thought

655
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:06,637
she would pass away at such
a young age and leave us...?

656
00:38:10,354 --> 00:38:11,589
I'm so foolish.

657
00:38:12,423 --> 00:38:13,758
With her personality,

658
00:38:14,225 --> 00:38:16,360
the palace was a prison to her.

659
00:38:20,531 --> 00:38:22,400
She was confined for so many years.

660
00:38:24,101 --> 00:38:25,101
Now,

661
00:38:26,037 --> 00:38:27,538
she's finally free.

662
00:38:33,210 --> 00:38:35,246
When I first saw you,

663
00:38:35,746 --> 00:38:37,682
I knew you were Tang'er's children.

664
00:38:39,216 --> 00:38:40,618
That day at Yanbo Tower,

665
00:38:41,285 --> 00:38:43,554
I really wanted to see Tang'er's children,

666
00:38:44,622 --> 00:38:46,424
so I approached your father.

667
00:38:48,859 --> 00:38:49,859
Aunt Lin.

668
00:38:50,761 --> 00:38:51,762
Actually, mother

669
00:38:52,797 --> 00:38:53,898
for all these years,

670
00:38:54,765 --> 00:38:56,400
has been thinking of you too.

671
00:38:57,435 --> 00:38:58,435
Really.

672
00:38:58,736 --> 00:39:00,371
Mother always treasured her handkerchief

673
00:39:00,404 --> 00:39:01,138
as if it were a precious gem.

674
00:39:01,405 --> 00:39:03,440
Before she left, she even told my brother

675
00:39:03,441 --> 00:39:04,709
to take good care of it.

676
00:39:05,409 --> 00:39:07,044
We just never knew

677
00:39:07,545 --> 00:39:09,647
what this handkerchief represented.

678
00:39:13,951 --> 00:39:14,951
So mother

679
00:39:15,386 --> 00:39:16,921
was once so helpless.

680
00:39:18,356 --> 00:39:19,657
I must not let such a tragedy

681
00:39:20,558 --> 00:39:22,827
happen again to Yanzhi and me.

682
00:39:24,261 --> 00:39:25,261
Today,

683
00:39:25,863 --> 00:39:27,998
Su He acted on his own to
seize my military talisman,

684
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:31,135
exposing his identity
without telling Yin Zhou.

685
00:39:31,769 --> 00:39:32,769
I think...

686
00:39:33,704 --> 00:39:34,972
He must have other intentions.

687
00:39:36,307 --> 00:39:37,307
You mean

688
00:39:37,875 --> 00:39:41,369
Su He's ambition is not
just to unify the grasslands...?

689
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:45,216
He dares to turn against me at this time,

690
00:39:45,950 --> 00:39:46,950
which means

691
00:39:47,918 --> 00:39:49,353
He intends to make all of us

692
00:39:50,142 --> 00:39:51,343
die in Jiangnan City.

693
00:39:52,556 --> 00:39:54,058
He's just dreaming.

694
00:39:54,959 --> 00:39:56,827
As long as I'm here in
Jiangnan for one day,

695
00:39:57,294 --> 00:39:58,294
this Jiangnan City

696
00:39:58,491 --> 00:40:00,585
will not allow him to stir up trouble.

697
00:40:01,799 --> 00:40:02,799
Senior,

698
00:40:03,100 --> 00:40:04,100
Nowadays,

699
00:40:04,502 --> 00:40:05,603
none of us knows

700
00:40:05,627 --> 00:40:06,866
when Yin Zhou will make a move.

701
00:40:08,239 --> 00:40:09,540
We need to be fully prepared.

702
00:40:10,274 --> 00:40:11,852
The imperial guards
at the imperial palace

703
00:40:11,876 --> 00:40:13,316
A Qi has already assigned personnel.

704
00:40:14,345 --> 00:40:15,856
The imperial palace is
of utmost importance.

705
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:18,949
It must be well arranged to let
trustworthy people protect the Emperor.

706
00:40:19,650 --> 00:40:20,850
I secretly transferred a troop

707
00:40:21,285 --> 00:40:21,919
from Talhan

708
00:40:22,153 --> 00:40:23,587
to Jiangnan this time.

709
00:40:24,121 --> 00:40:26,201
Plus the death squads
you've trained for me, senior,

710
00:40:28,125 --> 00:40:29,685
Yin Zhou may not have a winning chance.

711
00:40:30,294 --> 00:40:31,294
I'm afraid that

712
00:40:32,930 --> 00:40:34,610
Su He has some other tricks up his sleeve.

713
00:40:36,367 --> 00:40:39,069
Leave Su He's whereabouts to me.

714
00:40:40,638 --> 00:40:41,638
Royal brother,

715
00:40:41,739 --> 00:40:42,807
What can I do?

716
00:40:43,107 --> 00:40:44,241
Hearing you say this,

717
00:40:44,265 --> 00:40:45,299
I'm getting nervous.

718
00:40:45,476 --> 00:40:47,211
I also want to contribute to Daxing.

719
00:40:48,012 --> 00:40:49,012
You,

720
00:40:49,613 --> 00:40:51,549
just stay obediently
in the imperial palace.

721
00:40:52,950 --> 00:40:53,950
No.

722
00:40:54,462 --> 00:40:55,729
Stay in Yanbo Tower instead.

723
00:40:55,753 --> 00:40:56,787
It's safer here.

724
00:40:57,521 --> 00:40:58,823
As long as you're safe,

725
00:40:58,856 --> 00:41:00,136
I'll be grateful to the heavens.

726
00:41:01,158 --> 00:41:02,693
Why are you looking down on people?

727
00:41:02,893 --> 00:41:04,653
This princess has also
learned martial arts.

728
00:41:05,029 --> 00:41:06,109
The princess's martial arts

729
00:41:06,363 --> 00:41:07,864
are probably not even
enough to protect herself, right?

730
00:41:07,865 --> 00:41:08,132
You!

731
00:41:08,332 --> 00:41:09,332
Heshu,

732
00:41:09,355 --> 00:41:10,756
Follow your royal brother’s advice.

733
00:41:11,235 --> 00:41:12,369
Only when you're safe

734
00:41:12,937 --> 00:41:14,572
can he fully deal with Yin Zhou.

735
00:41:17,074 --> 00:41:18,074
It's getting late.

736
00:41:18,209 --> 00:41:19,276
We should go back.

737
00:41:19,877 --> 00:41:21,779
Right now, Yin Zhou thinks

738
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:24,240
that Yanzhi and I have
completely broken up.

739
00:41:24,448 --> 00:41:26,088
It's better for us to go back separately.

740
00:41:28,419 --> 00:41:29,419
Heshu,

741
00:41:29,820 --> 00:41:31,731
You go back to the imperial
palace with Yanzhi first.

742
00:41:31,755 --> 00:41:32,790
I'll go back later.

743
00:41:37,862 --> 00:41:38,862
Aunt Lin,

744
00:41:38,984 --> 00:41:40,185
I have a request.

745
00:41:41,432 --> 00:41:42,432
I hope Aunt Lin

746
00:41:42,533 --> 00:41:44,435
can agree to it for my mother's sake.

747
00:41:45,782 --> 00:41:46,816
Just say it.

748
00:41:48,906 --> 00:41:50,241
If Yin Zhou and Su He

749
00:41:51,208 --> 00:41:53,244
really join hands to rebel in Jiangnan,

750
00:41:54,078 --> 00:41:56,747
even though Yanzhi and I have
made thorough preparations,

751
00:41:57,882 --> 00:41:58,916
no one can predict

752
00:41:59,516 --> 00:42:00,718
what the outcome will be.

753
00:42:01,752 --> 00:42:06,156
If something happens to me,

754
00:42:06,690 --> 00:42:07,690
I hope Aunt Lin

755
00:42:08,292 --> 00:42:09,926
can take good care of Heshu for me.

756
00:42:09,927 --> 00:42:10,927
Okay.

757
00:42:10,961 --> 00:42:12,229
I promise you.

758
00:42:12,496 --> 00:42:14,164
You trust my aunt too little.

759
00:42:14,431 --> 00:42:15,833
Who's in charge of Jiangnan City?

760
00:42:15,966 --> 00:42:17,368
You can ask around on the streets.

761
00:42:18,269 --> 00:42:19,269
Xianyue,

762
00:42:20,104 --> 00:42:21,104
Don't be rude.

763
00:42:22,873 --> 00:42:24,575
I naturally believe in Aunt Lin's ability.

764
00:42:25,109 --> 00:42:26,109
It's just that

765
00:42:26,744 --> 00:42:28,784
we need to be prepared
for the worst in everything.

766
00:42:31,916 --> 00:42:32,916
Xianyue,

767
00:42:34,051 --> 00:42:36,487
Heshu hasn't had many
friends since she was a child.

768
00:42:37,354 --> 00:42:38,422
I can feel that

769
00:42:38,956 --> 00:42:39,956
you and her...

770
00:42:40,090 --> 00:42:41,090
Stop, stop.

771
00:42:41,325 --> 00:42:42,325
We, the martial arts folks,

772
00:42:42,326 --> 00:42:43,846
can't stand such sentimental requests.

773
00:42:44,628 --> 00:42:46,063
I don't have my aunt's broad mind

774
00:42:46,109 --> 00:42:47,710
to take in Yin Heshu for a lifetime.

775
00:42:47,923 --> 00:42:49,658
You'd better take care of her yourself.

776
00:42:57,508 --> 00:42:58,576
Thank you, Aunt Lin.

777
00:43:03,447 --> 00:43:04,447
No one saw us, right?

778
00:43:04,648 --> 00:43:05,648
Don't worry, A Qi.

779
00:43:06,450 --> 00:43:07,450
Today I saw

780
00:43:07,751 --> 00:43:09,429
you talking with Aunt Lin in the corridor.

781
00:43:09,453 --> 00:43:10,453
What did you talk about?

782
00:43:11,454 --> 00:43:12,855
Since Prince Pei is so smart,

783
00:43:12,890 --> 00:43:13,970
why don't you have a guess?

784
00:43:19,063 --> 00:43:20,063
I guess

785
00:43:21,865 --> 00:43:23,300
you still worry about Heshu.

786
00:43:27,705 --> 00:43:28,705
Yanzhi,

787
00:43:29,473 --> 00:43:30,473
even if in this life

788
00:43:30,574 --> 00:43:32,294
I can't change the outcome of my past life,

789
00:43:32,810 --> 00:43:34,411
I have no regrets.

790
00:43:35,813 --> 00:43:37,653
My mother has also been
sent back to Jiangnan.

791
00:43:37,815 --> 00:43:39,495
Heshu has also been entrusted to Aunt Lin.

792
00:43:39,817 --> 00:43:40,897
The most important thing is

793
00:43:41,719 --> 00:43:42,719
in this life,

794
00:43:42,853 --> 00:43:44,221
I know your feelings for me.

795
00:43:45,222 --> 00:43:46,222
I have no regrets.

796
00:43:48,659 --> 00:43:50,961
What if, in this battle,

797
00:43:51,829 --> 00:43:54,110
it's as tragic as what you
experienced in your past life?

798
00:43:55,165 --> 00:43:56,445
Are you still not afraid at all?

799
00:43:57,668 --> 00:44:00,938
As long as we recognize each
other and fight side by side,

800
00:44:01,405 --> 00:44:02,673
I'm not afraid of anything.

801
00:44:22,693 --> 00:44:25,295
Why am I still coughing up
blood after taking the antidote?

802
00:44:26,263 --> 00:44:27,263
No.

803
00:44:27,631 --> 00:44:28,798
I must get rid of Yin Zhou and Su He

804
00:44:28,799 --> 00:44:29,967
before I die

805
00:44:30,834 --> 00:44:33,037
and must not leave any
future troubles for A Qi.

806
00:44:43,113 --> 00:44:44,113
Your Highness,

807
00:44:46,905 --> 00:44:48,704
(All according to plan)

808
00:44:50,688 --> 00:44:51,822
Burn it.

809
00:44:52,690 --> 00:44:53,690
Yes.

810
00:44:55,726 --> 00:44:56,726
Fu'an,

811
00:44:56,927 --> 00:44:58,961
Do you know what kind of thing

812
00:44:58,962 --> 00:45:00,322
is suitable to do in such weather?

813
00:45:01,432 --> 00:45:02,533
This servant is foolish

814
00:45:02,566 --> 00:45:03,646
and naturally doesn't know.

815
00:45:04,168 --> 00:45:06,637
Since it's something the
Crown Prince wants to do,

816
00:45:07,071 --> 00:45:09,740
it must be a wonderful thing.

